\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bzk1665702559988.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bzk1665702559988.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bzk1665702559988.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bzk1665702559988\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $itemnr\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bzk1665702559988___itemnr_271193\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the list item that corresponds to a given index number in a list.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__topic_d85088e1_d85089e1_d85090e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__p_d85091e1_d85092e1_d85093e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$itemnr</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">N</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__topic_d56467e1_d56468e1_d56469e1_d56470e1_d56471e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1223848e82\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">N</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__3\">Sequence number. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8900e1_d8901e1_d8902e1__entry__3\">Uniface list from which to extract an\n                        item.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__topic_d56472e1_d56473e1_d56474e1_d56475e1_d56476e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1223848e151\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__p_d85100e1_d85101e1_d85102e1\">If the <var class=\"keyword varname\">N</var>th item is not found in <var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$itemnr</span> function returns NULL and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1129</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> after\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$itemnr</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__2\">\n Error Constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1129</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ITEM&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzk1665702559988__table_d8903e1_d8904e1_d8905e1__entry__3\">Item with the requested index is not found. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__topic_d56477e1_d56478e1_d56479e1_d56480e1_d56481e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1223848e238\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__topic_d56482e1_d56483e1_d56484e1_d56485e1_d56486e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1223848e248\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzk1665702559988__p_d85112e1_d85113e1_d85114e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$itemnr</span> function acts in the\n            same way as the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getitem</span> ProcScript statement, but can also be used as\n            part of an expression. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ayl1665702554178.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ayl1665702554178.html\" title=\"A list is a group of related items homogeneous items collected into a single unit, the list. Every item in a list is assumed to have the same structure.\">Lists and Sublists</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cip1665702554022.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>List Handling in ProcScript</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript instructions that enable you to build lists, retrieve items from lists, and sort lists based on various criteria.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gan1665702559756.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$idpart</a><p>Return the ID part of an associative list item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ytj1665702559912.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$valuepart</a><p>Return the value part of an associative list item.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526328\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526328\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$itemnr Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $itemnr Return the list item that corresponds to a given index number in a list. $itemnr ( N , List ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description N Numeric Sequence number. List String Uniface list from which to extract an item. Return Values If the N th item is not found in List , the $itemnr function returns NULL and $procerror is set to -1129 . Table 2. Values commonly returned in $procerror after $itemnr Value Error Constant Meaning -1129 <UPROCERR_ITEM> Item with the requested index is not found. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $itemnr function acts in the same way as the getitem ProcScript statement, but can also be used as part of an expression. For more information, see Lists and Sublists . Related Links List Handling in ProcScript Uniface provides ProcScript instructions that enable you to build lists, retrieve items from lists, and sort lists based on various criteria. $idpart Return the ID part of an associative list item. $valuepart Return the value part of an associative list item. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}